Class CacheEntry<T>

  lego.gracekelly.entities.CacheEntry<T>

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public final class CacheEntry<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The CacheEntry class is a simple java object that holds data required to get, put and invalidate a cache entry. The generic parameter indicates the type of the object that'll be store against the given key.
